sesp-desc: Adde certe proprietates extra special a tote le paginas
sesp-property-author-desc: "$1" registra tote le usatores que ha modificate un pagina. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-first-author-desc: "$1" registra le usator que ha create un pagina. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-revision-id-desc: "$1" registra le identificator de version actual de un pagina. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-page-id-desc: "$1" registra le ID de un pagina. Illo es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-page-len-desc: "$1" registra le longitude de un pagina in bytes. Illo es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-page-img-desc: "$1" registra le imagines de pagina (Extension:PageImages) de un pagina. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-view-count-desc: "$1" registra le numero de visitas de un pagina. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-subpages-desc: "$1" registra tote le subpaginas de un pagina. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-revisions-desc: "$1" registra le numero de versiones de un pagina. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-talk-revisions: Numero de versiones del pagina de discussion
sesp-property-talk-revisions-desc: "$1" registra le numero de versiones de un pagina de discussion. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-shorturl-desc: "$1" registra le URL curte de un pagina. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-approved-rev-desc: "$1" registra le ID del version de un pagina que ha essite approbate. Illo es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-namespace-id-desc: "$1" registra le ID del spatio de nomines de un pagina. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-namespace-name: Nomine canonic del spatio de nomines
sesp-property-namespace-name-desc: "$1" registra le nomine canonic del spatio de nomines de un pagina. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-approved-by-desc: "$1" registra le usator que ha definite le stato de approbation de un pagina. Illo es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-approved-date-desc: "$1" registra le hora al qual le stato de approbation del pagina ha essite definite. Illo es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-approved-status-desc: "$1" registra le stato de approbation de un pagina. Illo es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-user-registration-date-des: "$1" registra le data de inscription del usator. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-user-edit-count-desc: "$1" registra le numero de modificationes del usator. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-user-edit-count-per-ns: Numero de modificationes del usator per spatio de nomines
sesp-property-user-edit-count-per-ns-des: "$1" registra le numero de modificationes del usator in un certe spatio de nomines. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-user-edit-count-ns-desc: "$1" registra le numero del spatio de nomines in le registro del numero de modificationes del usator. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-user-edit-count-cnt-desc: "$1" registra le numero de modificationes in le registro del numero de modificationes del usator. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-user-block-desc: "$1" registra un lista de blocadas imponite a un usator. Illo es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-user-right-desc: "$1" registra un lista de derectos concedite a un usator. Illo es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-user-group-desc: "$1" registra un lista de gruppos applicate a un usator. Illo es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-property-exif-data-desc: "$1" registra le datos EXIF del file. Es fornite per le extension [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Extra_Special_Properties Semantic Extra Special Properties].
sesp-admin-deprecation-notice-title-repl: Le sequente section contine parametros que ha essite renominate o alteremente modificate e es recommendate actualisar immediatemente lor nomine o formato.
sesp-config-uses-fixed-tables: Configurar proprietates como proprietates fixe pro meliorar le accesso al datos
sesp-config-label-cache-version: Specifica un modificator de cache interne
sesp-config-exclude-bot-edits: Debe le modificationes proveniente de contos de usator in le gruppo "bot" esser ignorate quando se immagazina datos pro le proprietates special?
